OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 1 May to Sun 10 May
OL,6,FDuring this period, conditions will
OL,7,Fprobably be more changeable than they
OL,8,Fhave been recently, with low pressure
OL,9,Fsystems becoming more likely. This
OL,10,Fmeans an increasing chance of showers
OL,11,For longer spells of rain, with a risk
OL,12,Fof strong winds at times. Some dry
OL,13,Fspells with some warm sunshine are
OL,14,Fstill likely at times too, with a risk
OL,15,Fof a few short-lived early morning fog
OL,16,Fpatches. Temperatures are likely to be
OL,17,Fclose to or slightly above normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
